{"tid":1256201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不要捱打]數據話俾你知 我哋有贏嘅可能","createTime":"2019-06-25T01:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T05:15:35.000Z","uid":264079,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff1758dfdaf070e8283a32f6dfdeba726cacfda","tid":1256201,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"繼上一po後，<br />\n[真正戰場]200萬人登記哂做選民 保蝗黨都係贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254006</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽到唔同巴絲意見，話好多區都係自動當選。<br />\n除此之外，仲有啲建制議員做咗十幾廿年好難撼動<br />\n要喺度重申: 做得耐=/=做得好 或 勝任<br />\n試問除咗蛇齋餅糉外，你上次見區議員係幾時？<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n<br />\n而家用數據話俾你聽，我哋有機會贏<br />\n不過有個前設: <br />\n-夠多人登記做選民<br />\n-投票率要夠高，要俾市民知道投票係權利+義務<br />\n以屯門區2015區議會選舉為例:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZ9Ows3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZ9Ows3.png&h=45067547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，唔好意思小弟不才，淨係搵到2015區選資料對比2017年選民資料<br />\n減返2016,2017年新增選民數目<br />\n要當選基本上要該區3成選票左右，姑且當呢3成係鐵票，你睇616，200萬人大熱天時黑衫上街，要鼓動其餘7成唔係無機會。<br />\n<br />\n雖然而家每日有150嚟溝淡緊我哋，但係根據而家嘅政治氣氛，加埋本身會投非建制嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋絕對有機會翻盤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n覺醒吧 真。香港人<br />\n1. 登記做選民，叫埋身邊親戚朋友<br />\n2.即使有選民，都要有人企岀嚟，被人選先得。否則只會係有票無得投，建制自動當選<br />\n<br />\n招人參加區議會選舉 減少建制派自動當選（長文）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253475</a><br />\n<br />\n3.白區一定要岀選，你叫我除定褲俾人老強(自動當選)就勢係假<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，最好上埋fb <br />\n<br />\n有錯請指岀<br />\n<br />\n資料來源:<br />\n1.https://<a href=\"http://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/屯門區議會\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=83e5e063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/屯門區議會</a> ; 2.https://<a href=\"http://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/pdf/Age%20and%20Sex%20profile%20of%20registered%20electors%20by%20431%20District%20Council%20Constituency%20Areas%20in%202017PR_L.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FAge%2520and%2520Sex%2520profile%2520of%2520registered%2520electors%2520by%2520431%2520District%2520Council%2520Constituency%2520Areas%2520in%25202017PR_L.pdf&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=f97676e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.voterregistration.gov.hk/pdf/Age%20and%20Sex%20profile%20of%20registered%20electors%20by%20431%20District%20Council%20Constituency%20Areas%20in%202017PR_L.pdf</a><br />\n3.https://<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201511/23/P201511230156.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201511%2F23%2FP201511230156.htm&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=487313e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201511/23/P201511230156.htm</a>"},{"pid":"66c710854d81e89bfe9e080dceb13f3cff913d2e","tid":1256201,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"cfbae1e932bc153bc49e73fdfd1a27b0519ea790","tid":1256201,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e11427d43c0c1c48ed73f1e083ab1290607cdff2","tid":1256201,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"406a6b8b246a6de0cd95971c68b04a2051a9b894","tid":1256201,"uid":229225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:28:58.000Z","msg":"好文幫推<br />\n<br />\n大家記得 2/7 登記做選民!!"},{"pid":"8e69f4b12620d0b6019e6b735524bfe7f3033508","tid":1256201,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:29:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n1.做選民<br />\n2.提名人"},{"pid":"b7144e269a4c259e123e1cc29f6f31e417318fd6","tid":